A '''snow shed'''  or '''avalanche shed''' is a [[structure]] that provides [[avalanche]] protection for [[road]]s and [[rail tracks|railroad tracks]]. 

Depending on the threat level and size of area to be protected, they are built of wood or [[reinforced concrete]]

